How to toggle between two different icons
=============================================
Toggle the icon using the class attribute

Add a icon
----------

// click on an icon to run a function

<i onclick="myFunction(this)" class="fa fa-thumbs-up" style="margin-right: 15px;" id="mytitle"></i>


Create a script
----------------

<script>

function myFunction(x) {

    x.classList.toggle("fa-heart"); //toggle the icon from thumbs up to heart
   
     }
</script>
